(13,'1','/serves/images/1624525375471156373578464240069819194356.png','特斯拉','L1-020','1','<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">中山首个特斯拉体验中心，区别传统4S店模式，集体验、交付、售后服务于一体。提供汽车及零备件、周边产品展示、销售、试乘试驾体验、技术咨询、相关培训与活动等体验，提供汽车交付、维修、保养、检测、调试、设立电动汽车充电设备、设施等服务。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">特斯拉在全球一直坚持“官网电商+实体体验中心”的直营模式，体验中心则成为与消费者沟通的纽带。进入特斯拉体验中心，“产品专员”和顾问将用耐心的讲解和答疑让消费者感知到技术与创新，向人们普及最先进的纯电动智能汽车和全新的汽车拥有体验。</p><p><br/></p>','/serves/images/1624525407909236374434919994934922294016.jpg','配套,主力店','1','0','2021-6-24 17:1:47','T','615,419,25,21'),
(14,'4','/serves/images/1624525668621206374409848262053825486362.jpg','壹鼎点','L4-010A','1','<section>壹鼎点，是一家以经营&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #D6A841;\">精致点心</span></strong>、<span style=\"color: #D6A841;\"><strong>粤式烧味</strong></span>、<strong><span style=\"color: #D6A841;\">创意料理</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #D6A841;\">&nbsp;</span></strong>为主的新派时尚<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">餐厅，坐落于中山市东区中山六路1号天奕星河COCO City L4-010A。</span></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">是中山老</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">字号&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #D6A841; letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\"><strong>天天渔村小榄公饭店</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">在深耕本土30多年后，面向年轻一代而精心打造的</span><strong><span style=\"color: #D6A841; letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">全新餐饮品牌店</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">。</span></section><section><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">壹鼎点从年轻人的角度出发，颠覆以往就餐环境，设计了中式mix时尚、优雅而缤纷的餐厅风格，是潮流达人和年</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">轻白领用餐的时尚选择。</span></section><section><section><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.54px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">壹鼎点以全新的品牌形象出道，带来的不止是天天渔村小榄公